val crimeCountyDF = crimeCADF.join(agencyCountyDF, crimeCADF("Agency") === agencyCountyDF("agency"), "inner")
  .select("county",
          "Violent crime rate", 
          "Property crime rate",
          "year")
  .filter($"year" === 2014)
  .groupBy("county", "year")
  .agg(sum("Violent crime rate").as("violent_crime_rate"), sum("Property crime rate").as("property_crime_rate"))
